message.entry: Selection indices for cells must be a N-by-2 numeric array.
Selection indices for rows must be a 1-by-N numeric array.
Selection indices for columns must be a 1-by-N numeric array.
Selection indices are out of data boundary.
When 'Multiselect' is 'off', 'Selection' must be empty, or a scalar number for 'row' and 'column' selection type, or a 1-by-2 numeric array for 'cell' selection type.
